{"id": 1204, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在搜索信息的时候有什么困扰?", "description": "啊，搜什么关键词好呢？（题图来自：Harriet Taylor Seed）", "record_count": 2322, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160905151210ODIh9fC2gmW1qJo4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-09T03:00:16Z", "options": [{"id": 114432, "content": "回答长篇大论并且包含专业术语或带上计算公式，给我的感觉是我问了一个跟火箭上天一样正经的问题，小伙伴的认真真是把我感动到哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752475}, {"id": 114688, "content": "有时找不到我想要的答案，等于是没有回答我的问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753483}, {"id": 114944, "content": "没法搜一首路边听到的，只记得某个片段的调子的歌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754639}, {"id": 114433, "content": "有弹幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742305}, {"id": 114689, "content": "广告太多...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753483}, {"id": 114434, "content": "信息过时，或者搜到的是零散的相关字，但是内容没什么相关性", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724796}, {"id": 114435, "content": "想吃蓝莓结果别人塞一个毒草莓过来自己还不会分辨，吃了直接挂掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752495}, {"id": 114436, "content": "百度小黄图  各种小广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751392}, {"id": 114437, "content": "搜到的信息和资料都是过时的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744067}, {"id": 114438, "content": "我就想用google，天朝不让。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669880}, {"id": 114439, "content": "想搜的无法搜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752480}, {"id": 114440, "content": "404 not found", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488406}, {"id": 114441, "content": "搜竞争对手相同产品、会优先显示自家此类应用广告。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714103}, {"id": 114442, "content": "挺有意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752554}, {"id": 114443, "content": "很多信息需要专业的人解答，可以试试找腾讯行家^_^", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 502826}, {"id": 114444, "content": "搜到的非所问~~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 516619}, {"id": 114445, "content": "怎么才能变得心有长性？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752586}, {"id": 114446, "content": "搜索结果无法按照时间倒排序", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752599}, {"id": 114448, "content": "好奇心的关键词搜索就经常搜不到文章", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 393557}, {"id": 114960, "content": "广告过多，学术的信息太少", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692867}, {"id": 114449, "content": "不知道该查什么关键词", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752624}, {"id": 114450, "content": "对于自己喜欢的关键词进行搜索", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724174}, {"id": 114451, "content": "一些难以用关键词去搜索的消息，模糊界定，导致搜到的信息pia", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723513}, {"id": 114452, "content": "这个页面为什么没有可以跟别人做出的回答做互动的shezhin", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723513}, {"id": 114715, "content": "游泳健身請問需要瞭解一下嗎？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 61731}, {"id": 114462, "content": "感觉在做产品测试，模糊/精确搜索间交替，总害怕搜索引擎智商太低（事实就是那样的）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715493}, {"id": 114471, "content": "要放弃百度了，都是各种推广", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670125}, {"id": 152360, "content": "什么时候能穿墙而过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898058}, {"id": 114475, "content": "Google不能用啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118237}, {"id": 114733, "content": "太分散了，东一点西一点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753649}, {"id": 114480, "content": "广告推送太讨厌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743142}, {"id": 114482, "content": "被颠覆了世界观", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748544}, {"id": 114748, "content": "谷歌用不了，垃圾百度广告太多，其他搜索引擎信息量不够", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618956}, {"id": 117310, "content": "搜到的小学生不是小学生!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761977}, {"id": 117055, "content": "好人一生平安！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761050}, {"id": 114759, "content": "搜不到我想要的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 706046}, {"id": 118856, "content": "对专业名词了解太少，关键词找不准，搜不到想要的结果。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770195}, {"id": 114762, "content": "有太多广告，满屏都是，一不小心就点到了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752520}, {"id": 114509, "content": "用谷歌时，默认搜索引擎里加上 -site:baidu.com", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201889}, {"id": 114766, "content": "突然不知道该怎么表达自己想搜索的内容。而且广告一大堆，和自己意思不沾边的结果太多。好不容易有几个感觉靠谱的，一看时间~早就过期了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753771}, {"id": 114514, "content": "搜索关键词后总是弹出有关键词但不是自己想要的信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645829}, {"id": 115803, "content": "搜索引擎想让我们看什么，我们就能够看到什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075634}, {"id": 115292, "content": "移动端的页面总被小黄图挡住，关闭键也不好使，就跳转黄色网站，很无语", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709333}, {"id": 115553, "content": "换个意思相近的关键词出来的结果差的万里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732363}, {"id": 126567, "content": "几年前的问题几年前的回答", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805380}, {"id": 121707, "content": "只有广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784107}, {"id": 117615, "content": "广告猖狂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196054}, {"id": 117361, "content": "我要的找不到。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 762342}, {"id": 126840, "content": "特别是百度，坑爹的，每次搜这个，它总是要冒一些不相干的东西，浪费我流量！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806696}, {"id": 114553, "content": "太抽象 搜出来都是广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752847}]}